<h1>Help & Documentation</h1>

<p>Welcome to Invoicify! This page provides guidance for using the main features of the application.</p>

<h2>Invoice Browser</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Browse all invoices in a searchable, interactive table.</li>
    <li>Select an invoice to preview its details, including parties, items, and payment info.</li>
    <li>View QR codes for payment directly from the invoice details.</li>
    <li>Export invoices to HTML or PDF for sharing or record-keeping.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Invoice Creator</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Create new invoices or edit existing ones.</li>
    <li>Fill in seller and customer information, bank details, and QR payment data.</li>
    <li>Add orders and invoice items with detailed information.</li>
    <li>Use the "Clear all" button to reset the form, or fill with test data for quick setup.</li>
    <li>Save your invoice to add it to the system.</li>
</ul>

<h2>QR Generator</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Generate QR payment codes by entering payment details.</li>
    <li>Preview the QR code instantly as you fill out the form.</li>
    <li>Use the "Clear all" button to reset the QR form fields.</li>
</ul>

<p>If you need further assistance, please contact support or refer to the README documentation.</p>
